Provogue Men's Checkered Casual Shirt Price: Rs.800

Give a boost to your vibrant personality by donning this purple checkered casual shirt from the house of Provogue. This shirt is made of 100 per cent cotton and comes with full sleeves and contrast lined angled cuffs that can be rolled up according to your convenience. The diagonal placket and the darts at the back of this trendy shirt give you a smart look. The embroidery on the chest increases the charm of this Provogue Shirt.

Team this shirt with a pair of washed jeans and loafers and enjoy your shopping spree or your office outing. Intelligent designs
column17:
premium fabrics and vibrant hues come together in the collection of casual shirts from Provogue. The brand is lauded and admired for its cleverness with styles and expertise with fabrics.

Fabric Care

Gentle machine wash the shirt using cold water. Wash dark colours separately. Avoid bleaching. You can dry it inside out in the shade. Use warm iron on it to enjoy the crispness of cotton.
